==Mandarin==

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī rì wéi shī, zhōng shēn wéi fù

===Phrase===
'''[[一]][[日]][[为]][[师]],[[终]][[身]][[为]][[父]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') Even if someone is your teacher for only a day, you should regard him like your father for the rest of your life.

===Alternate forms===
[[一]][[日]][[為]][[師]],[[終]][[身]][[為]][[父]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

